data.description: New Price…..be in your next home in the New Year! Come visit a sweet slice of heaven at 140 Blue Jay Way, this wonderful home is nestled in the Southern Meadows community just a stone’s throw away from all things Hershey. This home boasts 5 bedrooms and 4.5 baths with enough room for you and yours. If you enjoy entertaining you will have many evenings and weekends ahead to enjoy cooking in your recently updated kitchen (2022) showcasing quartz countertops with an island, tiled backsplash and stainless steel appliances (2020-2023). Carry the fun outside to your upper level deck built for enjoyment and easy maintenance with TimberTech composite decking. No more yearly staining needed. Stairs lead to the lower level screened porch and stamped concrete patio with firepit. Smores anyone? More time for relaxing with family and friends surrounded by the sounds of nature and a lush greenbelt that provides privacy and minimal yard maintenance. During the winter and in times of snowfall, the gentle yard slopes on the side of the home offer the greatest in snow sledding for both young and old or during spring/summer awesome slip-n-slide set up to beat the heat. Who needs a boring swing set but there is room for that to. The exposed walkout and finished basement offers more indoor entertainment space for a game room, in-law or teen spaces with easy care luxury vinyl plank flooring, full bath and abundant storage. This house was built by the sellers and has been a wonderful place to raise their family and call HOME. It is now time for a new chapter and for another to be able to enjoy what they have through the years, making memories to last a lifetime. Schedule your private showing today and feel the warmth of HOME.
